{"lemma":"حِجابٌ","slug":"حِجابٌ","root":"ح.ج.ب","root_slug":"ح-ج-ب","root_link":"/words/roots/ح-ج-ب","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"حِجاب","root":"حجب","pos":"N","occurrence_count":7},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":7},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n7143"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AD%D9%90%D8%AC%D8%A7%D8%A8%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"screen, barrier","examples":[{"text":"وَمَا كَانَ لِبَشَرٍ أَنْ يُكَلِّمَهُ اللَّهُ إِلَّا وَحْيًا أَوْ مِنْ وَرَاءِ حِجَابٍ"}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"cover"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"curtain"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"diaphragm (also اَلْحِجَاب الْحَاجِز (al-ḥijāb al-ḥājiz))"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"amulet"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"headscarf, hijab"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"plural of حَاجِب (ḥājib)","tags":["form-of","plural"]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/ħi.d͡ʒaːb/","/ħi.ɡæːb/","/ħd͡ʒɑːb/","/ħi.ʒaːb/","/ħʒaːb/","/ħʒeːb/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n7143","headword_ar":"حِجَابٌ","root":"Hjb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A thing that prevents, hinders, debars,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"precludes:"},{"kind":"text","text":"] a"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thing that veils, conceals, hides, covers,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"protects;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, K TA;) because it prevents seeing, or beholding: (Msb:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a thing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, K,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"body."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that intervenes"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, Msb, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"between two things,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, K,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"between two bodies;"},{"kind":"text","text":"which is [said to be] the primary signification; (Msb;) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a partition, a bar, a barrier,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an obstacle:"},{"kind":"text","text":"] and sometimes applied to ideal things: (Msb:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jujubN","text_ar":"جُجُبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (A, Msb, K.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Duriba AlHijaAbu EalaY Aln~isaA='i","text_ar":"ضُرِبَ الحِجَابُ عَلَى النِّسَا=ءِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The veil,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"curtain, was put,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"let down, over the women"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (A, TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lahu daEawaAtN taxoriqu AlHujuba","text_ar":"لَهُ دَعَوَاتٌ تَخْرِقُ الحُجُبَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He has prayers that rend the veils"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (A, TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA lidaEowapi AlmaZoluwmi HijaAbN","text_ar":"مَا لِدَعْوَةِ المَظْلُومِ حِجَابٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"There is no veil,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"obstacle, to the prayer of the wronged"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (A, TA.) It is said in a trad.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mani A@T~alaEa AlHijaAbi waAqaEa maA","text_ar":"مَنِ ا@طَّلَعَ الحِجَابِ وَاقَعَ مَا"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waraA='ahu","text_ar":"وَرَا=ءَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He who gets sight and knowledge of the veil falls into that which is behind it"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: i. e., when a man dies, he falls into what is behind [one of] the two veils, that of Paradise and that of Hell: (ISh, TA:) or, accord. to some,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AiTalaAEu AlHijaAbi","text_ar":"اِطَلَاعُ الحِجَابِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"stretching out the head [and looking over the veil"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; for he who examines into a thing stretches out his head to see what is behind the veil, or covering. (TA.) And in another trad., a saying of Mohammad, (TA,)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_in~a A@ll~`ha yagofiru liloEabodi","text_ar":"اـِنَّ ا@للّٰهَ يَغْفِرُ لِلْعَبْدِ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA lamo yaqaEi AlHijaAbu","text_ar":"مَا لَمْ يَقَعِ الحِجَابُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Verily God forgiveth the servant"},{"kind":"text","text":"(his creature)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"as long as the precluding event shall not have happened"},{"kind":"text","text":"]:"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlHjAb","text_ar":"الحجاب"},{"kind":"text","text":"here meaning the dying in the belief in a plurality of gods: (K, * TA:) as though one were precluded from true belief by death. (TA.) One says also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlEajozu HajaAbN bayona AlA_inosaAni wamuraAdihi","text_ar":"العَجْزُ حَجَابٌ بَيْنَ الاـِنْسَانِ وَمُرَادِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Inability is a bar between man and his desire"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (Msb.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlmaEoSiyapu HijaAbN bayona AlEabodi wabayona rab~ihi","text_ar":"المَعْصِيَةُ حِجَابٌ بَيْنَ العَبْدِ وَبَيْنَ رَبِّهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Disobedience is a bar between the servant and his Lord"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (Msb.) ―         -b2-  [Hence, in the present day, (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A written charm"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"amulet;"},{"kind":"text","text":"generally worn in a case (called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bayotu","text_ar":"بَيْتُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HijaAbK","text_ar":"حِجَابٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":") suspended, on the right side, by a string passing over the left shoulder, or on some other part of the person: pl. of mult."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HujubN","text_ar":"حُجُبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and of pauc."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aHojibapN","text_ar":"اَحْجِبَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HijaAbaAtN","text_ar":"حِجَابَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] ―         -b3-  [Hence also,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A thin piece of flesh,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"resembling a piece of shin,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the interior of the body, between the two sides, intervening between the lungs and the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qSb","text_ar":"قصب"},{"kind":"text","text":"[in the K"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlqaSab","text_ar":"القَصَب"},{"kind":"text","text":", but this is evidently a mistranscription for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlquSob","text_ar":"القُصْب"},{"kind":"text","text":"the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lower intestines;"},{"kind":"text","text":"for the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HjAb","text_ar":"حجاب"},{"kind":"text","text":"is the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"diaphragm,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"midriff"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (K, TA:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HijaAbu Alqalobi","text_ar":"حِجَابُ القَلْبِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (A,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HajaAbu Aljawofi","text_ar":"حَجَابُ الجَوْفِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S,) signifies ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the same;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HajaAbu Alkabidi","text_ar":"حَجَابُ الكَبِدِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xilobN","text_ar":"خِلْبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":";)]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"what intervenes between the heart and the rest of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jwf","text_ar":"جوف"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the piece of skin that intervenes between the heart and the belly:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, TA:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HijaAbu Alqalobi","text_ar":"حِجَابُ القَلْبِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a certain fat that clothes the heart:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(AHeyth, TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$gf","text_ar":"شغف"},{"kind":"text","text":":) [or it signifies, or signifies also,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the septum cordis:"},{"kind":"text","text":"see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qalobN","text_ar":"قَلْبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":":] pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HujubN","text_ar":"حُجُبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, TA.) Hence the saying,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"hataka Alxawofu HijaAba qalobihi","text_ar":"هَتَكَ الخَوْفُ حِجَابَ قَلْبِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Fear rent open his midriff:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"his septum cordis"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (A, TA.) ―         -b4-  (assumed tropical:)  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"horizon:"},{"kind":"text","text":"[because it terminates the view:] so in the phrase,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tawaArato biA@loHijaAbi","text_ar":"تَوَارَتْ بِا@لْحِجَابِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It"},{"kind":"text","text":"(the sun)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became concealed by the horizon;"},{"kind":"text","text":"occurring in the Kur [xxxviii. 31], and in a trad. (TA.) ―         -b5-  (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A mountain:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an elevated part of a mountain."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaEada fiY Zil~i AlHijaAbi","text_ar":"قَعَدَ فِى ظِلِّ الحِجَابِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He sat in the shade of the mountain."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A.) ―         -b6-  (assumed tropical:)  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"place where a [stony tract such as is called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Har~ap","text_ar":"حَرَّة"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ends."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) ―         -b7-  (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A tract of sand uniformly continuous, and long."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) ―         -b8-  (assumed tropical:)  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"light"},{"kind":"text","text":"of the sun: or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tract,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"side,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of the sun: (K, TA:) or [like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaAjibN","text_ar":"حَاجِبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a side,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"part,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of the sun. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["Msb","A","K","ISh","TA","S"]}]},"classical_definitions":{"source":"hawramani","url":"https://arabiclexicon.hawramani.com/%D8%AD%D8%AC%D8%A7%D8%A8/","headword_ar":"حجاب","entries":[{"lexicon_id":"dictionary_18","lexicon_en":"Al-Sharīf al-Jurjānī, Kitāb al-Taʿrīfāt (d. 1413 CE)","lexicon_ar":"كتاب التعريفات للشريف الجرجاني","permalink":"https://arabiclexicon.hawramani.com/?p=23208#9f4d74","body_html":"<span>الحجاب: كل ما يستر مطلوبك، وهو عند أهل الحق: انطباع الصور الكونية في القلب المانعة لقبول تجلي الحق.<br></span><br><div>حجاب العزة: هو العمى والحيرة؛ إذ لا تأثير للإدراكات الكشفية في كنه الذات، فعدم نفوذها فيه حجاب لا يرتفع في حق الغير أبدًا.</div>"}]}}